#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:79
msgid ""
"Converted ModelOpt FP8 checkpoints should be loaded as transformer component "
"overrides. If the repo or local directory already contains `config.json`, "
"use `--transformer-path`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:83
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev \\\n"
"  --transformer-path lmsys/flux2-dev-modelopt-fp8-sglang-transformer \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A Logo With Bold Large Text: SGL Diffusion\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:91
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"  --transformer-path lmsys/wan22-t2v-a14b-modelopt-fp8-sglang-transformer "
"\\\n"
"  --prompt \"a fox walking through neon rain\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:101
msgid ""
"`--transformer-path` is the canonical flag for converted ModelOpt FP8 "
"transformer component repos or directories that already carry `config.json`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:103
msgid ""
"If the override repo or local directory contains its own `config.json`, "
"SGLang reads the quantization config from that override instead of relying "
"on the base model config."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:106
msgid ""
"`--transformer-weights-path` still works when you intentionally point at raw "
"weight files or a directory that should be metadata-probed as weights first."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:108
msgid "`dit_layerwise_offload` is supported for ModelOpt FP8 checkpoints."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:109
msgid "`dit_cpu_offload` still stays disabled for ModelOpt FP8 checkpoints."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:110
msgid ""
"The layerwise offload path now preserves the non-contiguous FP8 weight "
"stride expected by the runtime FP8 GEMM path."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:112
msgid ""
"On disk, the quantization config stays `quant_method=modelopt` with "
"`quant_algo=FP8`; the `modelopt-fp8` label in this document is a support "
"family name, not a serialized config key."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:115
msgid ""
"To build the converted checkpoint yourself from a ModelOpt diffusers export, "
"use `python -m sglang.multimodal_gen.tools.build_modelopt_fp8_transformer`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:118
msgid "ModelOpt NVFP4"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:122
msgid ""
"For mixed ModelOpt NVFP4 transformer overrides that already contain `config."
"json`, keep the base model and quantized transformer separate and use `--"
"transformer-path`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:126
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-dev \\\n"
"  --transformer-path lmsys/flux1-dev-modelopt-nvfp4-sglang-transformer \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A Logo With Bold Large Text: SGL Diffusion\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:134
msgid ""
"For raw NVFP4 exports such as the official FLUX.2 release, use `--"
"transformer-weights-path`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:137
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev \\\n"
"  --transformer-weights-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4 \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A Logo With Bold Large Text: SGL Diffusion\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:145
msgid ""
"SGLang also supports passing the NVFP4 repo or local directory directly as "
"`--model-path`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:148
msgid ""
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4 \\\n"
"  --prompt \"A Logo With Bold Large Text: SGL Diffusion\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:155
msgid ""
"For a dual-transformer Wan2.2 export where only the primary `transformer` "
"was quantized:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:158
msgid ""
"SGLANG_DIFFUSION_FLASHINFER_FP4_GEMM_BACKEND=cudnn \\\n"
"sglang generate \\\n"
"  --model-path Wan-AI/Wan2.2-T2V-A14B-Diffusers \\\n"
"  --transformer-path lmsys/wan22-t2v-a14b-modelopt-nvfp4-sglang-transformer "
"\\\n"
"  --prompt \"a fox walking through neon rain\" \\\n"
"  --save-output\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:169
msgid ""
"Use `--transformer-path` for mixed ModelOpt NVFP4 transformer repos or local "
"directories that already include `config.json`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:171
msgid ""
"Use `--transformer-weights-path` for raw NVFP4 exports, individual "
"safetensors files, or repo layouts that should be treated as weights first."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:173
msgid ""
"For dual-transformer pipelines such as `Wan2.2-T2V-A14B-Diffusers`, the "
"primary `--transformer-path` override targets only `transformer`. Use a per-"
"component override such as `--transformer-2-path` only when you "
"intentionally want a non-default `transformer_2`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:177
msgid ""
"On Blackwell, the validated Wan2.2 ModelOpt NVFP4 path currently prefers "
"FlashInfer FP4 GEMM via `SGLANG_DIFFUSION_FLASHINFER_FP4_GEMM_BACKEND=cudnn`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:180
msgid ""
"This environment-variable override is a current workaround for NVFP4 cases "
"where the default sglang JIT/CUTLASS `sm100` path rejects a large-M shape at "
"`can_implement()`. The intended long-term fix is to add a validated CUTLASS "
"fallback for those shapes rather than rely on the override."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:184
msgid ""
"Direct `--model-path` loading is a compatibility path for FLUX.2 NVFP4-style "
"repos or local directories."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:186
msgid ""
"If `--transformer-weights-path` is provided explicitly, it takes precedence "
"over the compatibility `--model-path` flow."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:188
msgid ""
"For local directories, SGLang first looks for `*-mixed.safetensors`, then "
"falls back to loading from the directory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:190
msgid ""
"To force the generic diffusion ModelOpt FP4 path onto a specific FlashInfer "
"backend, set `SGLANG_DIFFUSION_FLASHINFER_FP4_GEMM_BACKEND`. Supported "
"values include `flashinfer_cudnn`, `flashinfer_cutlass`, and "
"`flashinfer_trtllm`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../diffusion/quantization.md:193
msgid ""
"On disk, the quantization config stays `quant_method=modelopt` with "
"`quant_algo=NVFP4`; the `modelopt-nvfp4` label here is again a documentation "
"family name rather than a serialized config key."
msgstr ""

